The =localize= instance method of the =Uize.Widget= base class has been improved with support for a new optional =tokenNamingSTR= parameter.

The new optional =tokenNamingSTR= parameter allows for greater flexibility in token naming syntax (eg. square bracket enclosed tokens like =[tokenName]=, angle bracket enclosed tokens like =&lt;tokenName&gt;=, percent symbol enclosed tokens like =%tokenName%=, or anything that suits your application).



